'''Return to Ridu: Together in a New Chapter''' is a [[Web Event|Web]] [[Event]] in [[Version 2.8]].

==Event Details==
===Duration===
* 2026/06/06 20:00 (UTC+8) – 2026/07/17 03:59:59 (server time)
* The rewards cannot be claimed after the event is over, so don't forget to claim them.

===Event Details===
* During the event, invite friends to return or register for the game to receive up to Polychrome ×340.
* Join the lucky draw on the webpage for a chance to win a PS5, figures, merch, and tons of Polychromes!
* After a New Proxy links an invitation code, they need to reach Inter-Knot level 10.
* The "Return to Ridu: Together in a New Chapter" web event will close on 2026/07/17 at 03:59:59 (server time). Proxies, make sure to participate before it ends!

===Reward Preview===
{{Card List|Polychrome; Senior Investigator Log; W-Engine Energy Module; Official Investigator Log; W-Engine Power Supply; Bangboo Algorithm Module; Denny}} 

===Event Rewards===
* PlayStation®5 ×5
* [[Anby]] Demara 1/7 Scale Figure ×10
* Framed Acrylic Standee Set - [[Ye Shunguang]] ×60
* Bangboo Standee Figurine Surprise Box Vol. 2 ×200

===How are New, Returning, and Inactive Proxies determined in this event?===
# New Proxies: Proxies who register a new Zenless Zone Zero account during the "Return to Ridu: Together in a New Chapter" event, and whose registration date is less than 14 days prior to participating in the event.
# Returning Proxies: Proxies who have returned to the game after being offline for ≥14 consecutive days.
# Inactive Proxies: Proxies who have been offline for 14 consecutive days or more, have logged into the "Return to Ridu: Together in a New Chapter" event page, but have not yet returned to the game.
* During the "Return to Ridu: Together in a New Chapter" event, even if a Proxy activates their Returning Proxy status multiple times, they can only link one invitation code, and the event page data will be retained.

